you can definitely do it, and I will always help you earn money to eat more local specialties, nyaa!","(Where did the stupid rabbit and Wanjirou sneak off to, nyaa... They said they would help out as well, nyaa!!)","Unlockable Buildings: {0}","Notepad","Special Event - Bamboo Cloud Festival\n8/19/2024 – 1/7/2025 1:59 P.M. (UTC-7)\n\nBamboo Cloud, the famous Chamber of Commerce in One Han City, is going to celebrate its anniversary. We warmly invite you to be part of this special occasion.\nHead to Champion Street and assist Fuuka Minami with the anniversary preparations. Enjoy delightful stories and immerse yourself in the festivities!\n\nDuring the event, you can acquire a limited Illustration by participating for the first time. Collecting all 8 Mementos will earn you an additional illustration!\n\nAbout Buildings and Mementos\n- Different buildings have unique festive stories. Tap on locked buildings to receive more information!\n- Complete Chapter 3 of each building to receive Mementos.\n- Depending on your decision, Festival Incidents will have different outcomes. Investigate the hidden secrets and collect all the Mementos!\n\nAbout Accountant\'s Rewards\n- Complete the stories of each building to receive rewards. Don\'t forget to collect, nyaa!","Unlock","Complete the prior chapter to unlock","Mementos","Complete a different ending in Chapter 3 to receive","Story Summary","Unlock Story","Mission List","Memento Box","Story in Progress","Story Review","Story Locked","Complete a different ending in Chapter 3 of {0} to receive","Congratulations, you acquired all the Mementos, and the Bamboo Cloud Festival has reached a successful end!","Locked","This building\'s stories are unavailable. Please stay tuned.","Go to Event","Go to Shop - Outfit?","Special Prize","Grand Prize","The pulled prizes will not return to the prize pool, pull 30 times to get the Special Prize.","Mystery Gacha - Collab Edition is here!\nMahjong Soul Shrine\'s mystery gacha machine reappears in a new look!\nComplete daily event missions to get gacha tokens (except matches played against AI)\nUse gacha tokens to pull for prizes in the machine!\n\n*You will get a prize with each gacha pull and the prizes will not return to the prize pool.\n*Pull 30 times to get the Special Prize.","Jiaobei","Throw Jiaobei","Sheng","Yin","Xiao","Question","Obtain Evidence","Investigation Progress","Unknown","Evidence Bag","Evidence Acquired","Investigate","Current Popularity","Playing Ranked Match or Event Match to gain Popularity.","Collab Limited Event - Shiny Concerto\nEvent Period: 11/24 after maintenance - 12/15 1:59 P.M. (UTC-7)\n\nNoctchill, the super popular idol group, arrived in One Han City by accident. They now need to perform a live concert and build up enough popularity here before heading to their planned next stop.\nHelp the idols win over the citizens in a more localized way!\n\nDuring the event, you can accumulate Popularity by playing Ranked Match or Event Match. Completing [Missions] grants you Cupcakes, which can be used to Level Up skills and enhance the efficiency of obtaining Popularity.\nWhen you reach the required Popularity, you can claim Summon Scroll, Collab-limited Illustration, and Sage\'s Bag as rewards from [Rewards] on the event page!\nWhen a certain time arrives, you can view the idols\' wonderful journey from [Story] on the event page.\n\nAbout Popularity\nObtain Popularity by playing Ranked Match or the event match, Limitless Asura.\n\nPopularity obtained in 4-player match\n1st place: +16000\n2nd place: +9600\n3rd place: +4800\n4th place: +1600\nPopularity obtained in 3-player match\n1st place: +9600\n2nd place: +4800\n3rd place: +1600\n\nWinning (below Mangan): +2500\nWinning (Mangan): +5000\nWinning (Haneman): +7000\nWinning (Baiman): +10000\nWinning (Sanbaiman): +15000\nWinning (Yakuman and above): +20000","Current Popularity","Close","Event Match","Special Rules: Limitless Asura\n- Before the tile distribution, all players will have a replacement tile in their hand.\n- The replacement tile cannot be discarded, used for Chii/Pon/Kan, or exchanged with other players.\n- The replacement tile can be considered any tile except a red Dora (including as the 5th tile of a kind)\n- When the replacement tile is counted as a Dora, it follows the usual Han Bonus calculation.\n- When winning, the replacement tile will be calculated in a way that maximizes the hand\'s value (excluding Ura Dora).\n- After the Hand distribution, select 3 tiles and exchange them with other players.\n- The ending condition of each match has been changed from 1 winner to 3 winners.\n- Upon winning, the points will be calculated in real-time, and the tiles in hand will remain hidden. The match will end when a player is busted.\n- When a match ends, and there are less than 3 winners, it is regarded as a Draw.\n- There will be no Repeat Counter, regardless of whether the dealer has achieved Tenpai, the next match starts from 0 Repeat Counter.\n- When Draw happens during the match, regardless of whether there are winners, the match will restart from 0 Repeat Counter.\n- In the same match, players who have already won will not be participating in the Draw settlement.\n- When Draw happens, players who have not achieved Tenpai will pay 1000 points to each Tenpai player.\n- Players can choose to win when achieving Robbing a Kan (including Thirteen Orphans Concealed Quad). When a player wins by achieving Robbing a Kan, the Kan holds.\n- When Four-Kan Abortion happens after Robbing a Kan, Robbing a Kan holds, and the match will restart due to the Draw during the match.\n- Deal-in while in Riichi.\n- If the points left are above 1000 after paying for deal-in, the Riichi holds.\n- If the points left are below 1000 after paying for deal-in, the Riichi fails, and the match continues.\n- If the points left are below 0 after paying for deal-in, the match ends.\n- Player doesn\'t have to pay responsibility for causing other players\' Big Three Dragons or Four Big Winds.\n\nMatch mode: Limitless Asura - 4-Player East\nRank Limit: None\nEntry Limit: 5000 Coppers\nExchange Rate: 1000 Points=100 Coppers\nEntry Fee: 1000 Coppers\nMatches played in this mode are not ranked\nCasual Chest Progress: 1st+260, 2nd+130, 3rd+95, 4th+60\nBond Point Bonus: 40\nYou will receive Coppers if you finish with positive match points, or lose Coppers if you finish in negativity.","A replacement tile with limitless possibilities. \nAsura now evolves once again!\nExperience the thrilling 4-Player East matches!","Start","Cancel","Matchmaking...","Event Story","Event Missions","Event Rewards","Popularity bonus for the first 2 matches daily: {0}%","Popularity bonus for the rank in Ranked Match/Event Match: {0}%","Popularity bonus for winning in Ranked Match/Event Match: {0}%","Shiny Concerto event is now available! Go to [Event Match] to experience Limitless Asura, the match with special rules! During the event, you can obtain Popularity by playing the Event Match or Ranked Match!","During the event, complete [Missions] to obtain Popularity and Cupcakes. Use Cupcakes to [Level Up], and enhance the efficiency of obtaining Popularity!","Increase the Popularity to raise your Level. You can claim rich rewards including Summon Scroll and Limited Illustration. Don\'t miss out!","You can review event story at [Story].","All Redeemed","Earn double Coppers in the next move","Earn half Coppers in the next move","Double the number of steps in the next move","Halve the number of steps in the next move","Received Coppers on the map","Kaavi\'s Fortune Dial has come into effect","Winter is here! One Han City is hosting a magnificent winter fair, the Winter Wonderland. Join Yuan Xiao in this fun-filled event!\n\nEvent Period: 2024/12/18 - 2025/01/07 1:59 P.M. (UTC-7)\n\nComplete daily event missions to get dice (except matches played against AI).\nComplete specified number of laps on the event map to collect event rewards.\n\nUse dice to accumulate EXP 