step","Spring Festival Event - Lucky Spring Fair\nEvent Period: 1/20 - 2/13 1:59 P.M. (UTC-7)\n\nAt the dawn of the new year, the powerful snake god, along with her private attendant, moves into the Snake Palace, turning it into a popular spot in One Han City.\nPeople of all ages come here to write down their wishes, hoping for good fortune.\nAssist the mysterious attendant in managing the spring temple fair.\n\nDuring the event, complete wishes and raise the Fair Rank to earn various rewards including exclusive Tablecloth, Spring Festival Emote, Summon Scroll, Event Illustration, and more!\n\nAbout Wishes\n- Completing wishes will affect Fair Stats (positively or negatively). Each arrow stands for 10 pt.\n- How much Fair Stats increase or decrease will be affected by the result of the completed wishes, and some skills can affect their success rate!\n- Wishes can be obtained by finishing Missions.\n\nAbout Fair Rank\n- Fair Rank is linked to three Fair Stats: Fun, Status, Bond.\n- When these Fair Stats meet the upgrade requirements, the Fair Rank will go up and more rewards will be unlocked.\n\nAbout Incidents\n- When the Fair Rank goes up, some special incidents will occur and completing them will increase the Fair Stats greatly!\n- Depending on your decision, the incidents will have different outcomes.\n- It is said that when the Fair Rank reaches its highest, you will discover the attendant\'s hidden secrets.\n\nAbout Skills\n- Use Divine Power to upgrade the skills and enhance their effects.\n- Some skills will only be unlocked when you have reached a certain Fair Rank.\n- Divine Power can be obtained by finishing Missions.\n\nIchihime\'s Reminder\n- Proper allocation of Divine Power is the key to boosting efficiency.\n- Master, don\'t worry! If any wishes don\'t turn out well, I will comfort the worshipers, nyaa!","1/20 - 2/13 1:59 P.M. (UTC-7)","Left to handle: {0}","The offerings have piled up...","Rewards","Upgrade","Fair Rank","Incidents unlocked","Not enou